{"sections":[{"backgroundImage":"ic_theme_intro.png","estimatedTimeInMinutes":10,"chapter":"Go further with more ressources","kind":"hero","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since you have learned how OUDS works with theme, themeable view, components, tuning and view modifiers, it is time now to discover some online resources."}]}],"image":"ic_theme_intro.png","title":"Going further with more resources"},{"kind":"tasks","tasks":[{"contentSection":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Xcode can use the Swift DocC documentation of OUDS, and this documentation is used to build a static web site.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"But there are also other resources which can be useful for you.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"contentAndMedia","mediaPosition":"trailing"}],"title":"More resources","anchor":"More-resources","stepsSection":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The iOS technical documentation is available online. It has been generated from all the Swift DocC documentation written in the Swift Package.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You will find several catalogs (as many as librairies) with details about everyhting: components, tokens, themes, providers, etc.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-1.png","type":"step","caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can get it at ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The whole design system is documented and available online. You can find everything about components, tokens, guidelines and principles of OUDS."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"icon finder","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" is also available there to get icons for your projects."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-2.png","type":"step","caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Go to the website and learn things at ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"type":"step","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDS iOS provides also a wiki attached to its GitHub repository. The wiki is a public base of knowledge with plenty of things: available API, technicala architecture, tips about processes, tests, conventions and toolings.","type":"text"}]}],"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Have a look "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" to discover how OUDS works.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-3.png"},{"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-4.png","code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To get the source code of this showcase app, go to its dedicated GitHub repository at ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios-design-system-toolbox","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]}],"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For technical reasons the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" GitHub repository does not embed the source code of the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"design system toolbox","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" app. In fact this app and all its snapshots for tests increases a lot the size of the repository.","type":"text"}]}]},{"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-5.png","code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Do not 